'''郝久古桥''' ({{lang-fa|'''پل خواجو '''}} ''Pol-e Khāju'') 是[[伊朗|伊朗]][[伊斯法罕|伊斯法罕]]的一座桥梁，被誉为伊斯法罕省最优秀的桥梁。<ref name=andrew>{{cite book|title=Iran|author=Andrew Burke, Mark Elliot|publisher=Lonely Planet|year=2008|pages=243|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gEca_4iSNCUC&pg=PA243&dq=khaju+bridge&hl=en&ei=kNmHTciGA4GugQe6yvy3DQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDAQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=khaju%20bridge&f=false|access-date=2016-01-30|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610143506/https://books.google.com/books?id=gEca_4iSNCUC&pg=PA243&dq=khaju+bridge&hl=en&ei=kNmHTciGA4GugQe6yvy3DQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDAQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=khaju%20bridge&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

它是由[[波斯|波斯]][[萨非王朝|萨非王朝]]国王[[阿拔斯二世_(波斯)|阿拔斯二世]]于1650年左右，兴建在旧桥的基础上。它连接北岸的郝久区和Zayandeh河对岸的[[拜火教|拜火教]]区。它不仅是桥梁和水坝，还是一座建筑<ref>{{cite book|title=Developments in structural form|author=Rowland J. Mainstone|publisher=Architectural Press|year=2002|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qbdnVEd5nukC&pg=PT268&dq=khaju+bridge&hl=en&ei=kNmHTciGA4GugQe6yvy3DQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=7&ved=0CEYQ6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=khaju%20bridge&f=false|access-date=2016-01-30|archive-date=2016-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160511013252/https://books.google.com/books?id=qbdnVEd5nukC&pg=PT268&dq=khaju+bridge&hl=en&ei=kNmHTciGA4GugQe6yvy3DQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=7&ved=0CEYQ6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=khaju%20bridge&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，为公众集会的场所。<ref name=andrew/> 最初它装饰着艺术瓷砖和画作，用作茶馆。在建筑的中心，里面有一个凉亭，阿拔斯国王曾坐在这里，欣赏美景。<ref name=andrew/> 这座桥是[[萨非王朝|萨非王朝]]时期波斯建筑最好的例子之一。用厄珀姆·波普和让·夏尔丹的话说，郝久古桥是“波斯桥梁建筑的终极纪念碑和现存最有趣的桥梁之一...这里的整体具有节奏感，结合了最幸福的一致性：实用，美观和娱乐”<ref>{{cite book|title=A Journey to Persia: Jean Chardin's portrait of a seventeenth-century empire|author=Sir John Chardin, Ronald W. Ferrier|publisher=I.B.Tauris|year=1996|pages=149|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5CLkDgmVs1QC&pg=PA149&dq=khaju+bridge&hl=en&ei=kNmHTciGA4GugQe6yvy3DQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=khaju%20bridge&f=false|access-date=2016-01-30|archive-date=2016-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502195100/https://books.google.com/books?id=5CLkDgmVs1QC&pg=PA149&dq=khaju+bridge&hl=en&ei=kNmHTciGA4GugQe6yvy3DQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=khaju%20bridge&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

郝久古桥有24个拱门，长133米，宽12米。现有的铭文表明，大桥于1873年修复。

[[亚瑟·厄珀姆·波普|亚瑟·厄珀姆·波普]]和他的妻子菲利斯·阿克曼的陵墓就在附近。

